{"tid":448013,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助] 私處有魷魚味","createTime":"2017-10-25T23:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T05:59:34.000Z","uid":83993,"like":28,"dislike":123,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"10f9a5d93c3ba7bb49d0ee29b962eaa9c5de4c55","tid":448013,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:53:23.000Z","msg":"如果私處有異味 --&gt; d 味好似魷魚<br />\n如果性興奮出水時 --&gt; d 味好似魷魚, 海水<br />\n<br />\n其實同另一半開心時, 我都幾尷尬...<br />\n成日有味... 大家都聞到...<br />\n雖然陣味唔係話難接受, 但, 的確幾濃味...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想問有冇人知呢 d 係天生味濃的問題, 定係自己衛生方面做得唔夠??<br />\n我唔係突然間變到有味的, 係由青春期開始已經係咁...<br />\n<br />\n 其實我都日日有用護墊、沖涼有用私處清潔液...<br />\n但, 沖完涼之後, 好快又開始有味... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇sis同我一樣? 我又點先可以改善到, 唔要魷魚味?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5db888a8ad7c16ec5376de08b6951f5b7061b7","tid":448013,"uid":59898,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2b16fb3f5b690d5e540f3be485c9a4475ec6e5","tid":448013,"uid":70195,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:55:50.000Z","msg":"性病黎冇得醫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0534d3962c6e76a1a1a3400c0381136e42c29b56","tid":448013,"uid":57486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e879e32befc077dd1a4c2bf70a2d0f0a707bed9","tid":448013,"uid":3302,"like":132,"dislike":6,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:56:21.000Z","msg":"正一臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39100dba9dd9ae83807